Matrix Based Security in Jenkins

A table/matrix where you:
├── Rows    = Users
└── Columns = Permissions

How it looks:

User          | Build | View | Configure | Delete | Admin
------------- |-------|------|-----------|--------|------
Anonymous     |  ❌   |  ✅  |    ❌     |   ❌   |  ❌
john(dev)     |  ✅   |  ✅  |    ❌     |   ❌   |  ❌
jane(lead)    |  ✅   |  ✅  |    ✅     |   ✅   |  ❌
admin         |  ✅   |  ✅  |    ✅     |   ✅   |  ✅


