      ↓
Security
      ↓
Authorization
      ↓
Select "Matrix-based security"


|                 | Matrix Based         | Role Based              |
| --------------- | -------------------- | ----------------------- |
| **Setup**       | Per user permissions | Group roles then assign |
| **Best for**    | Small teams          | Large teams             |
| **Manage**      | Hard (many users)    | Easy (manage roles)     |
| **Flexibility** | High                 | Medium                  |


